'''普爾'''（{{lang-en|'''Poole'''}}，{{IPAc-en|audio=en-uk-Poole.ogg|p|uː|l}}）是位於[[英國|英國]][[多塞特郡|多塞特郡]]沿海的大型市鎮，位於[[多爾切斯特_(多塞特郡)|多爾切斯特]]以東{{convert|33|km|mi}}，與東部的[[伯恩茅斯|伯恩茅斯]]毗鄰。當地議會為[[普爾區議會|普爾區議會]]，1997年成為單一管理區，從[[多塞特郡議會|多塞特郡議會]]獨立。2001年人口138,288人，是多塞特郡第二大人口聚集地。它和伯恩茅斯、[[克萊斯特徹奇_(多塞特郡)|克萊斯特徹奇]]一起組成人口40萬的[[東南多塞特郡組合都市|東南多塞特郡組合都市]]。

普爾的人類活動記錄可追溯到[[鐵器時代|鐵器時代]]，而鎮名最早出現於12世紀，并開始成為重要貿易港，以繁榮的[[羊毛|羊毛]]貿易著稱。18世紀成為英國最繁榮的港口之一。[[二戰|二戰]]時期是[[諾曼第登陸|諾曼第登陸]]的主要出發點之一。

普爾的[[普爾港|天然港]]、燈塔和[[藍旗海灘|藍旗海灘]]提供了該鎮大部份的旅遊收入。[[伯恩茅斯交響樂團|伯恩茅斯交響樂團]]和[[皇家救生艇協會|皇家救生艇協會]]總部也位於普爾，[[皇家海軍|皇家海軍]]在此有基地。此地高等教育機構則有[[伯恩茅斯藝術大學|伯恩茅斯藝術大學]]和[[伯恩茅斯大學|伯恩茅斯大學]]。

==歷史==
{{Main|普爾歷史}}
[[File:Poole_Logboat.jpg|thumb]]
該地的名字來自於[[古英語|古英語]]“pōl”，意為靠近池塘小溪的地方。<ref name="Place names">{{cite book|title=A Dictionary of British Place-Names|url=http://www.oxfordreference.com/view/10.1093/acref/9780199609086.001.0001/acref-9780199609086-e-10503?rskey=3XHbEH&result=10640|last=Mills|first=A.D.|year=2003|publisher=Oxford University Press|location=Oxford|isbn=0-19-852758-6|access-date=2013-11-25|archive-date=2019-05-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190529053829/https://www.oxfordreference.com/view/10.1093/acref/9780199609086.001.0001/acref-9780199609086-e-10503?rskey=3XHbEH&result=10640|dead-url=no}}</ref>普爾現在所在地點周圍有2,500多年的人類居住史。在公元前3世紀，[[凱爾特人|凱爾特人]]的一支[[杜羅特里吉人|杜羅特里吉人]]從[[梅登城堡_(多塞特郡)|梅登城堡]]和[[Badbury_Rings|Badbury Rings]]移居至[[弗洛姆河_(多塞特郡)|弗洛姆河]]和[[普爾港|普爾港]]一帶。<ref>Cullingford (p.183)</ref>[[羅馬不列顛|羅馬人]]在1世紀[[羅馬征服不列顛|征服不列顛]]時曾在此的登陸并接管了一個位於位於今鎮中心以西的[[哈姆斯沃西|哈姆斯沃西]]的聚居點。<ref>Legg (p.9)</ref>在[[盎格魯-撒克遜|盎格魯-撒克遜]]時期，普爾屬於[[韋塞克斯|韋塞克斯]]王國，此時已被用作港口。<ref name="Welcome to Poole1">{{cite web | title = The Story of Poole (Page 1) | publisher = Welcome to Poole | year = 2008 | url = http://www.welcometopoole.co.uk/history/story1.htm | accessdate = 20 July 2008 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080622121754/http://www.welcometopoole.co.uk/history/story1.htm | archive-date = 2008-06-22 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>Guthrum和[[卡紐特大帝|卡紐特大帝]]分別在876年和1015年兩次侵佔該地。<ref>Sydenham (p.69–71)</ref><ref>Legg (p.13)</ref>

[[諾曼征服不列顛|諾曼征服不列顛]]之後，[[韋勒姆|韋勒姆]]的重要性衰退，普爾港開始繁榮起來。<ref>{{cite web | year = 2008 | url = http://www.wareham-tc.gov.uk/WTC_pages/wtc_history.htm#topofpage | title = History of Wareham | publisher = Wareham Town Council | accessdate = 17 July 2008 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110107095832/http://www.wareham-tc.gov.uk/WTC_pages/wtc_history.htm#topofpage | archive-date = 2011-01-07 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>當時普爾屬於一個貴族[[莊園|莊園]]，但在[[末日審判書|末日審判書]]中並不專門列出。<ref>Legg (p.14)</ref>最早的提及普爾的書面記錄出現於1196年，用以描述在“La Pole”建立的圣詹姆斯教堂。<ref>Legg (p.15)</ref>1248年，[[莊園主|莊園主]]William II Longespée頒佈普爾市民自由憲章，以為其參加[[第七次十字軍|第七次十字軍]]籌款。<ref name="Welcome to Poole1"/>於是封建制度下的普爾擁有了一小部份的自由，市民有權任命市長并組成法庭。1433年，[[亨利六世_(英格蘭)|亨利六世]]授予該鎮以staple port之地位，使得該港可以出口羊毛并開始修建城牆。<ref>Sydenham (p.94)</ref>1568年，普爾獲得更大的自治權，得以從多塞特郡獨立，并依據[[伊莉莎白一世|伊莉莎白一世]]的大憲章成立[[郡社團|郡社團]]（county corporate）。<ref name="historyof">{{cite web | title = History of Poole | publisher = Borough of Poole | year = 2008 | url = http://www.boroughofpoole.com/go.php?structureID=U464057c6c52db&ref=S4649D38C61551 | accessdate = 30 May 2008 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100105050439/http://boroughofpoole.com/go.php?structureID=U464057c6c52db&ref=S4649D38C61551 | archive-date = 2010-01-05 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>在[[英國內戰|英國內戰]]期間，因普爾[[清教徒|清教徒]]的立場及商人對[[造船費|造船費]]稅的反抗導致該鎮向[[圓顱黨|圓顱黨]]效忠。<ref>Legg (p.31)</ref>內戰中普爾並沒受到太大的戰火威脅，1646年[[保皇黨|保皇黨]]人在附近的[[考夫堡|考夫堡]]擊敗被捕。<ref name="Welcome to Poole3">{{cite web | title = The Story of Poole (Page 3) | publisher = Welcome to Poole | year = 2008 | url = http://www.welcometopoole.co.uk/history/story3.htm | accessdate = 20 July 2008 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080615142545/http://www.welcometopoole.co.uk/history/story3.htm | archive-date = 2008-06-15 | dead-url = yes }}</ref><ref>Sydenham (p.127–128)</ref>

[[File:Beech_Hurst,_Poole.JPG|thumb]]

16世紀普爾與[[英屬美洲|英屬美洲]]殖民地有密切商業往來，其中包括[[紐芬蘭與拉布拉多|紐芬蘭]]的漁商。<ref name="historyof"/>但是其最繁榮時期在18世紀早期，并一直持續到19世紀早期。此時的普爾海運主要是一個三角路線，即送糧食及鹽到紐芬蘭‘將紐芬蘭的鹹魚帶回歐洲，再將歐洲的葡萄酒、橄欖油和鹽運往普爾。<ref name="beamish8">Beamish (p.8–11)</ref>18世紀早期的主要交易對象是[[北美|北美]]，普爾有大批商人在此期間發家。<ref name="phc history">{{cite web | year = 2008 | url = http://www.phc.co.uk/about_history.html | title = The Harbour's History | publisher = Poole Harbour Commissioners | accessdate = 30 June 2008 | archive-date = 2019-05-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190523224828/https://www.phc.co.uk/about_history.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>因此當地建築業受到了影響，很多中世紀建築被換成[[喬治亞式建築|喬治亞式建築]]以及[[排屋|排屋]]。<ref name="beamish8"/><ref name="cockle">{{cite web | year = 2008 | url = http://www.pooletourism.com/go.php?structureID=pages&keywords=cockle&ref=I483ED26E32D39 | title = Poole Cockle Trail | publisher = Poole Tourism | accessdate = 3 September 2008 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110715103454/http://www.pooletourism.com/go.php?structureID=pages&keywords=cockle&ref=I483ED26E32D39 | archive-date = 2011-07-15 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>[[拿破崙戰爭|拿破崙戰爭]]和[[1812年戰爭|1812年戰爭]]結束了英國對紐芬蘭漁業的壟斷，因此普爾港也迅速衰退。<ref>Sydenham (p.398–402)</ref><ref name="Welcome to Poole4">{{cite web | title = The Story of Poole (Page 4) | publisher = Welcome to Poole | year = 2008 | url = http://www.welcometopoole.co.uk/history/story4.htm | accessdate = 23 May 2008 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080512021810/http://www.welcometopoole.co.uk/history/story4.htm | archive-date = 2008-05-12 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>而作為淺水港的普爾港也開始漸漸不能適應更大的船隻。<ref name="phc history"/>

在[[工業革命|工業革命]]期間，普爾鎮開始城市化，[[重商主義|重商主義]]盛行并充斥著大量貧民。普爾的第一鐵路站臺[[漢姆沃斯鐵路站|漢姆沃斯鐵路站]]建成於1847年，1872年鐵路延伸到市中心。<ref name="Welcome to Poole4"/>而相對海運的不景氣，普爾附近的沙灘和風景開始吸引各地遊客前來參觀，旅遊業便興盛起來，雖然其旅遊業一直比不上附近市鎮發達，但伯恩茅斯興盛的旅遊業使得普爾的商品製造業獲得了發展機會。<ref name="dorset page">{{cite web | year = 200 | url = http://www.thedorsetpage.com/locations/Place/P100.htm | title = Poole, Dorset, England | publisher = The Dorset Page | accessdate = 18 July 2008 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130730045423/http://www.thedorsetpage.com/locations/place/P100.htm | archive-date = 2013-07-30 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>

在[[二戰|二戰]]期間，普爾是[[D-Day|D-Day]]登陸的第三大出發點，併為歐洲的[[同盟國_(第二次世界大戰)|同盟國]]提供補給。<ref name="historyof"/>戰中該鎮大部份都遭到了德軍轟炸機的襲擊，二戰後更加衰敗。主要的[[城市更新|城市更新]]計劃發起於1950和60年代，大量[[貧民窟|貧民窟]]被清除，改建現代化建築。然而很多有悠久歷史的建築也遭到了拆除。1975年市中心成立保護區以保存普爾的歷史性建築。<ref name="Welcome to Poole5">{{cite web | title = The Story of Poole (Page 5) | publisher = Welcome to Poole | year = 2008 | url = http://www.welcometopoole.co.uk/history/story5.htm | accessdate = 23 May 2008 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080509062412/http://www.welcometopoole.co.uk/history/story5.htm | archive-date = 2008-05-09 | dead-url = yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title = The Built Environment | publisher = Borough of Poole | year = 2008 | url = http://poolelocalplan.wisshost.net/text/text5.htm#PolicyBE_1 | accessdate = 20 July 2008 | archive-date = 2013-10-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131006011518/http://poolelocalplan.wisshost.net/text/text5.htm#PolicyBE_1 | dead-url = no }}</ref>

==地理==

普爾位於[[英吉利海峽|英吉利海峽]]沿岸，環繞[[普爾港|普爾港]]東部和北部，距離[[倫敦|倫敦]]西南西{{convert|179|km|mi}}。該鎮最古老的部份處在普爾港的Holes Bay東南部。不過普爾港東部的大多數地區在20世紀中葉都進行了再開發。西部是[[厄普頓_(多塞特郡)|厄普頓]]和[[科夫馬倫|科夫馬倫]]，北部則是[[斯陶爾河_(多塞特郡)|斯陶爾河]]。 南部就是[[普爾灣|普爾灣]]，有著長達{{convert|4.8|km|mi}}的沙灘。

普爾下轄數個村莊和[[村鎮|村鎮]]：
[[奧爾德尼_(多塞特郡)|奧爾德尼]] – [[貝爾伍德_(多塞特郡)|貝爾伍德]] – [[布蘭克瑟姆_(多塞特郡)|布蘭克瑟姆]] – [[布蘭克瑟姆公園|布蘭克瑟姆公園]] – [[布羅德斯通_(多塞特郡)|布羅德斯通]] – [[坎福德懸崖|坎福德懸崖]] – [[坎福德荒野|坎福德荒野]] – [[Creekmoor|Creekmoor]] – [[Fleetsbridge|Fleetsbridge]] – [[漢姆沃斯|漢姆沃斯]] – [[利特利普_(普爾)|利特利普]] – [[Longfleet|Longfleet]] – [[Merley|Merley]] – [[新鎮_(多塞特郡)|新鎮]] – [[奧克達_(多塞特郡)|奧克達]] – [[帕克斯通|帕克斯通]] – [[Penn_Hill|Penn Hill]] – [[Sandbanks|Sandbanks]] – [[Sterte|Sterte]] – [[Talbot_Village|Talbot Village]] – [[威利斯頓|威利斯頓]] – [[滑鐵盧_(多塞特郡)|滑鐵盧]] – [[Whitecliff|Whitecliff]]

[[File:Dorset_geology.png|thumb]]粘土]]
普爾主要地貌是低地石南荒原。由於城市發展的緣故，這些自然景觀都遭到了一定成的破壞，不過當地還是有零散的[[特別保護地區|特別保護地區]]。地質則是不牢固的[[始新世|始新世]]粘土層（主要是[[倫敦粘土|倫敦粘土]]和[[重粘土|重粘土]]）和砂石。<ref name="dorsetgeology">{{cite web | year = 2006 | url = http://www.soton.ac.uk/~imw/Field-Guides-Introduction.htm | title = Geology of the Central South Coast of England | publisher = [[University_of_Southampton|University of Southampton]] | accessdate = 14 August 2007 | archive-date = 2007-08-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20070824120245/http://www.soton.ac.uk/~imw/Field-Guides-Introduction.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref>[[弗洛姆河_(多塞特郡)|弗洛姆河]]流經普爾，將脆弱的地表劃分成一塊塊河口平原。河口處有嘴狀沙洲。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.soton.ac.uk/~imw/Sandbanks.htm | title = Sandbanks Sand Spit | publisher = School of Ocean and Earth Science, [[University_of_Southampton|University of Southampton]] | accessdate = 5 August 2008 | archive-date = 2020-02-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200214015554/http://www.soton.ac.uk/~imw/Sandbanks.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref>

普爾港是歐洲最大的天然港，是僅次於[[傑克遜港|傑克遜港]]的世界第二大天然港。<ref>{{cite web | year = 2008 | url = http://www.boroughofpoole.com/environmental/services/ref:S4651BE26C4E36/aka:Harbour/ | title = Harbour | publisher = Borough of Poole | accessdate = 30 June 2008 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080706011158/http://www.boroughofpoole.com/environmental/services/ref%3AS4651BE26C4E36/aka%3AHarbour/ | archive-date = 2008-07-06 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>普爾港有著極高的生態重要性，此地的[[鹽鹼灘|鹽鹼灘]]和[[泥沼|泥沼]]為許多種[[候鳥|候鳥]]提供了棲息之所，同時也是[[具特殊科學價值地點_(英國)|具特殊科學價值地點]]、[[濕地公約|濕地公約]]特別保護地區和[[傑出自然風景區|傑出自然風景區]]。<ref name="port"/>普爾港極淺、面積約有{{convert|38|km2|sqmi}}，主要航運通道深為{{convert|7.5|m|ft|}}，港口平均深度為{{convert|48|cm|ft|}}。<ref name="dredge">{{cite web | year = 2008 | url = http://www.poolebay.net/PhaseI/dredging.htm | title = The Dredging Operation | publisher = PooleBay.net | accessdate = 3 June 2008 | archive-date = 2018-06-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180608012738/http://www.poolebay.net/PhaseI/dredging.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | year = 2008 | url = http://www.diadfish.org/maj2006_fichiers/maj_11_06_slime/piddle_and_frome.pdf | title = Rivers Piddle and Frome, and Poole Harbour | publisher = [[Centre_for_Environment,_Fisheries_and_Aquaculture_Science|Centre for Environment, Fisheries and Aquaculture Science]] | format = PDF | accessdate = 30 June 2008 | archive-date = 2021-02-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210225041547/http://www.diadfish.org/maj2006_fichiers/maj_11_06_slime/piddle_and_frome.pdf | dead-url = no }}</ref>普爾還包含數個島嶼，其中最大的是[[白浪島|白浪島]]。該島是[[童軍運動|童軍運動]]發源地。<ref name='Why Brownsea'>{{cite book | last = Woolgar | first = Brian| coauthors = La Riviere, Sheila | year = 2002 | title = Why Brownsea? The Beginnings of Scouting | publisher = Brownsea Island Scout and Guide Management Committee (re-issue 2007, Wimborne Minster: Minster Press)}}</ref>英國最大的陸上[[油田|油田]]位於海港南部。<ref name=bp2>{{cite web|url=http://www.bp.com/liveassets/bp_internet/globalbp/STAGING/global_assets/downloads/U/uk_asset_wytch_farm.pdf|title=BP Asset Portfolio: Wytch Farm|publisher=[[BP_plc|BP plc]]|accessdate=27 June 2008|format=PDF|archive-date=2007-10-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071011111645/http://www.bp.com/liveassets/bp_internet/globalbp/STAGING/global_assets/downloads/U/uk_asset_wytch_farm.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=andrews>Andrews I.J. & Balson P.S. (1995), ''Wight: Sheet 50N 02W Solid Geology'', 1:250,000 Geological map series, Keyworth: [[British_Geological_Survey|British Geological Survey]].</ref>

普爾以東是[[UNESCO|UNESCO]]世界遺產[[侏羅紀海岸|侏羅紀海岸]]，有著豐富的[[化石|化石]]。<ref name="jurassiccoast"/>[[西南海岸步道|西南海岸步道]]從薩默塞特郡[[邁恩黑德|邁恩黑德]]延伸至此，長達{{convert|1014|km|mi}}，是英格蘭最長的國家步道。<ref name="SWcoastpath">{{cite web | year = 2006 | url = http://www.southwestcoastpath.com/other-national-trails/ | title = Other National Trails | publisher = [[South_West_Coast_Path|South West Coast Path]] | accessdate = 5 December 2012 | archive-date = 2015-09-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150906234254/http://www.southwestcoastpath.com/other-national-trails/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>

