===氣候===
由於坐落在英格蘭南岸，普爾的氣候全年都很溫和。1971年至2000年的年平均溫度在10.2 至 12 [[°C|°C]]（50.4 到 53.6 [[°F|°F]]）之間。<ref name="annualmean">{{cite web | year = 2001 | url = http://www.metoffice.gov.uk/climate/uk/averages/19712000/tmean/17.gif | title = Mean Temperature Annual Average | publisher = [[Met_Office|Met Office]] | accessdate = 30 May 2008 | archive-date = 2012-02-22 | archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/65eCD6Fra?url=http://www.metoffice.gov.uk/climate/uk/averages/19712000/tmean/17.gif | dead-url = yes }}</ref>最暖的月份是七月和八月，平均氣溫為{{convert|12|-|22|C|F}}，最冷月為一月和二月，平均氣溫為{{convert|2|-|8.3|C|F}}。<ref name="annualweather">{{cite web | year = 2008 | url = http://weather.uk.msn.com/monthly_averages.aspx?wealocations=wc:UKXX0113 | title = Weather Averages Poole, England | publisher = [[Msn.com|Msn.com]] | accessdate = 30 May 2008 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110714125935/http://weather.uk.msn.com/monthly_averages.aspx?wealocations=wc:UKXX0113 | archive-date = 2011-07-14 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>[[海水表面溫度|海水表面溫度]]在二月間平均為{{convert|6.9|°C|°F|1}}，八月間為{{convert|18.5|°C|°F|1}}。<ref name="seatemperatures">{{cite web | year = 2006 | url = http://www.cefas.co.uk/data/sea-temperature-and-salinity-trends/presentation-of-results/station-23-bournemouth.aspx | title = Cefas Station 23: Bournemouth | publisher = [[Cefas|The Centre for Environment Fisheries & Aquaculture Science]] | accessdate = 30 May 2008 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080612052900/http://www.cefas.co.uk/data/sea-temperature-and-salinity-trends/presentation-of-results/station-23-bournemouth.aspx | archive-date = 2008-06-12 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>平均年降雨量為{{Convert|592.6|mm|in}}，低於英國平均年降雨量{{convert|1126|mm|in}}。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.metoffice.gov.uk/climate/uk/averages/19712000/areal/uk.html | title=UK 1971–2000 averages | publisher=[[Met_Office|Met Office]] | year=2008 | accessdate=12 October 2008 | archive-date=2009-07-05 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090705140124/http://www.metoffice.gov.uk/climate/uk/averages/19712000/areal/uk.html | dead-url=yes }}</ref>

