相對多塞特郡其他地區來說，普爾的經濟發展比較平衡。<ref name="profile">{{cite web | year = 2004 | url = http://poolelocalplan.wisshost.net/text/text2.htm | title = A Profile of Poole | publisher = Borough of Poole | accessdate = 2 June 2008 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131005004301/http://poolelocalplan.wisshost.net/text/text2.htm | archive-date = 2013-10-05 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>1960年代[[第二產業|第二產業]]開始繁榮，1980和90年代[[第三產業|第三產業]]後來居上。<ref name="profile"/>雖然自60年代以來製造業就業人數一直處於下降中，但在2002年仍有17%的普爾人就職于製造業。<ref name="profile"/>世界最大的[[豪華遊艇|豪華遊艇]]製造商[[聖汐克|聖汐克]]總部位於普爾，在當地[[船塢|船塢]]有超過1,800名僱員。<ref>{{cite web | title = The name's Sunseeker | publisher = [[Bournemouth_Daily_Echo|Bournemouth Daily Echo]] | year = 2006 | url = http://www.bournemouthecho.co.uk/search/display.var.990854.0.the_names_sunseeker.php | doi = | accessdate = 3 June 2008 }}</ref>2004年為當地經濟貢獻1.6億英鎊。<ref>{{cite web | year = 2004 | url = http://www.superyachttimes.com/editorial/14/article/id/107 | title = Sunseeker embarks on major expansion in Poole | publisher = Super Yacht Times | accessdate = 3 June 2008 | archive-date = 2016-01-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160105034554/http://www.superyachttimes.com/editorial/14/article/id/107 | dead-url = no }}</ref>其他大型製造廠包括[[Sealed_Air|Sealed Air]]、[[Mathmos|Mathmos]]、[[西門子公司|西門子]]和[[Ryvita|Ryvita]]等。普爾有東南多塞特郡最大的[[工業區|工業區]]。<ref name="industrial">{{cite web | year = 2004 | url = http://www.investindorset.co.uk/poole.html | title = Town Profile – Poole | publisher = Invest in Dorset | accessdate = 3 June 2008 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080820163658/http://www.investindorset.co.uk/poole.html | archive-date = 2008-08-20 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>

[[File:Poole.sunseeker.arp.jpg|thumb]]船塢]]

服務業也是普爾的支柱產業，大量員工就職于當地住戶服務經濟和旅遊業部門。1970年代普洱的低限制[[區域規劃|區域規劃]]政策使得許多倫敦的工廠搬遷至該地，<ref name="profile"/>例如一些銀行和經融服務公司。而實際上[[巴克萊銀行|巴克萊銀行]]最初的總部就位於普爾。[[默林娛樂|默林娛樂]]公司總部也坐落於此。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.blooloop.com/KBArticle/Merlin-Entertainments-Group/8 | title = Merlin Entertainments Group | year = 2008 | publisher = Blooloop.com | accessdate = 4 August 2008 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20081122043443/http://www.blooloop.com/KBArticle/Merlin-Entertainments-Group/8 | archive-date = 2008-11-22 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>海豚購物中心（Dolphin Shopping Centre）是多塞特郡最大的市內購物中心。<ref name="shops">{{cite web | url = http://www.pooletourism.com/go.php | title = Shopping | publisher = Poole Tourism | year = 2008 | accessdate = 26 July 2008 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080928074759/http://www.pooletourism.com/go.php | archive-date = 2008-09-28 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>旅遊業的重要性也不可忽視，2002年當地旅遊業收入達1.58億英鎊。<ref name="profile"/>而主要景點則是普爾港、碼頭、瓷器場和海灘。<ref name="jurassiccoast">{{cite web | year = 2006 | url = http://www.jurassiccoast.com/279/visiting-the-coast-31/gateway-towns-146/poole-457.html | title = Poole | publisher = [[Jurassic_Coast|Jurassic Coast]] | accessdate = 3 June 2008 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120911234317/http://www.jurassiccoast.com/279/visiting-the-coast-31/gateway-towns-146/poole-457.html | archive-date = 2012-09-11 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>

[[File:Barclays,_Poole.jpg|thumb]]

1970年左右，爲了繼續發展海運，普爾投資新建了港口建築并加深了航道，使得跨[[英吉利海峽|海峽]]貨運及客運流量增加。<ref name="profile"/>普爾港也是英國許多進口[[散裝貨|散裝貨]]的進口港。<ref name="port">{{cite web | year = 2006 | url = http://www.ecoports.com/ContentFiles/poole%20harbour%20aquatic%20management%20plan%202006.pdf | title = Poole Harbour Aquatic Management Plan 2006 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/5oI8ev2zN?url=http://www.ecoports.com/ContentFiles/poole%20harbour%20aquatic%20management%20plan%202006.pdf | archivedate = 2010-03-17 | publisher = EcoPorts | format = PDF | accessdate = 3 June 2008 }}</ref>當地有定期往返[[瑟堡|瑟堡]]、[[聖馬洛|聖馬洛]]和[[海峽群島|海峽群島]]的商業遊輪。<ref name="port"/>1954年[[皇家海軍|皇家海軍]]建立駐地RM Poole。<ref>{{cite web | year = 2008 | url = http://www.royalmarines.mod.uk/server/show/nav.6693 | title = The History of RM Poole | publisher = [[Ministry_of_Defence_(United_Kingdom)|Ministry of Defense]] | accessdate = 30 June 2008 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080604201947/http://www.royalmarines.mod.uk/server/show/nav.6693 | archive-date = 2008-06-04 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>此外普爾港也是一個重要的漁港。<ref name="fish1">{{cite web | title = Fishermen cast into a part-time role by quotas | publisher = [[Bournemouth_Daily_Echo|Bournemouth Daily Echo]] | year = 2008 | url = http://www.bournemouthecho.co.uk/search/display.var.2145594.0.fishermen_cast_into_a_parttime_role_by_quotas.php | accessdate = 3 June 2008}}</ref>當地的漁船隊是英國最大的業內船隊之一，<ref name="fish2">{{cite web | year = 2006 | url = http://www.phc.co.uk/downloads/channeldeepening/es10_fishing.pdf | title = Fishing Activity | publisher = Royal Haskoning | format = PDF | accessdate = 3 June 2008 | archive-date = 2019-05-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190524133548/https://www.phc.co.uk/downloads/channeldeepening/es10_fishing.pdf | dead-url = no }}</ref>然而由於燃油費和[[歐盟|歐盟]]的[[共同漁業政策|共同漁業政策]]，這隻船隊已經開始衰退。<ref name="fish1"/><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.bournemouthecho.co.uk/mostpopular.var.2353782.mostviewed.fishermen_protest_as_fuel_costs_strike_hard.php | title = Fishermen protest as fuel costs strike hard | year = 2008 | publisher = [[Bournemouth_Daily_Echo|Bournemouth Daily Echo]] | accessdate = 4 August 2008}}</ref>

==教育==
普爾有十六所[[一級學校|一級學校]]、八所中學、七所一體學校、八所中等學校和[[語法學校|語法學校]]、五所[[特別學校|特別學校]]、兩所[[獨立學校_(英國)|獨立學校]]和一所[[繼續教育|繼續教育]]學院。較著名的[[坎福德學院|坎福德學院]]是一所由當地教育部門管理的[[寄宿學校|寄宿學校]]，兩所語法學校則是要求嚴格的精英中學。[[普爾高中|普爾高中]]是當地最大的中學，約有學員1,660人。<ref name="local info">{{cite web | year = 2007 | url = http://localinfo.dorsetecho.co.uk/li/ | title = Local information for Poole | publisher = [[Dorset_Echo|Dorset Echo]] | accessdate = 23 June 2008 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080613005621/http://localinfo.dorsetecho.co.uk/li/ | archive-date = 2008-06-13 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>[[伯恩茅斯和普爾學院|伯恩茅斯和普爾學院]]是全英最大的繼續教育學院，為多塞特郡提供學術及短期教育。<ref>{{cite web | year = 2007 | url = http://www.ofsted.gov.uk/oxedu_reports/download/(id)/87857/(as)/50785_301133.pdf | title = Ofsted Inspection | publisher = [[Ofsted|Ofsted]] | accessdate = 23 June 2008 | format = PDF | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20081031014227/http://www.ofsted.gov.uk/oxedu_reports/download/%28id%29/87857/%28as%29/50785_301133.pdf | archive-date = 2008-10-31 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>

2007年普爾的[[英國普通中等教育證書|英國普通中等教育證書]]成績在英格蘭148個地區排名第8。<ref>{{cite news | year = 2007 | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/education/7180228.stm | title = How different areas performed | publisher = BBC News | accessdate = 23 June 2008 | date = 10 January 2008 | archive-date = 2008-12-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20081223235525/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/education/7180228.stm | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="gcse tables">{{cite web | year = 2007 | url = http://www.dcsf.gov.uk/cgi-bin/performancetables/group_07.pl?Mode=Z&No=836&Base=b&Type=LA&Phase=1&Year=07 | title = Secondary School achievement and attainment tables 2007 | publisher = [[Department_for_Children,_Schools_and_Families|Department for Children, Schools and Families]] | accessdate = 23 June 2008 | archive-url = http://webarchive.nationalarchives.gov.uk/20091024095009/http%3A//www.dcsf.gov.uk/cgi%2Dbin/performancetables/group_07.pl?Mode%3DZ%26Type%3DLA%26No%3D836%26Base%3Db%26Phase%3D1%26Year%3D07 | archive-date = 2009-10-24 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>[[帕克斯通語法學校|帕克斯通語法學校]]成績最好，其全部學生都得到了全部為C級以上的成績。普爾高中只有39%，而最差的羅斯摩爾社區學院（Rossmore Community College）只有19%。<ref name="gcse tables"/>普爾語法學校在[[A-level|A-level]]成績上也有出色表現。<ref name="local info"/><ref name="alevel tables">{{cite web | year = 2007 | url = http://www.dcsf.gov.uk/cgi-bin/performancetables/group_07.pl?Mode=Z&No=836&Base=a&Type=LA&Phase=2&Year=07 | title = School and college (post-16) achievement and attainment tables 2007 | publisher = [[Department_for_Children,_Schools_and_Families|Department for Children, Schools and Families]] | accessdate = 23 June 2008 | archive-url = http://webarchive.nationalarchives.gov.uk/20091014010051/http%3A//www.dcsf.gov.uk/cgi%2Dbin/performancetables/group_07.pl?Mode%3DZ%26Type%3DLA%26No%3D836%26Base%3Da%26Phase%3D2%26Year%3D07 | archive-date = 2009-10-14 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>

[[伯恩茅斯大學|伯恩茅斯大學]]是一所在1992年獲得大學資格的[[新大學|新大學]]，主校區位於普爾。<ref>{{cite web | year = 2008 | url = http://www.boroughofpoole.com/go.php?ref=S46779A7387179&structureID=U46713df2215ff | title = Bournemouth University | publisher = Borough of Poole | accessdate = 23 June 2008 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20081201161410/http://www.boroughofpoole.com/go.php?structureID=U46713df2215ff&ref=S46779A7387179 | archive-date = 2008-12-01 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>其強項是媒體相關專業。<ref>{{cite web | year = 2008 | url = http://www.bournemouth.ac.uk/about/introduction_to_bu/welcome.html | title = Welcome to Bournemouth University | publisher = [[Bournemouth_University|Bournemouth University]] | accessdate = 23 June 2008 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080330022422/http://www.bournemouth.ac.uk/about/introduction_to_bu/welcome.html | archive-date = 2008-03-30 | dead-url = yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | year = 2008 | url = http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/life_and_style/education/good_university_guide/article2166314.ece | title = Profile: Bournemouth University | publisher = The Times | accessdate = 23 June 2008 | location = London | first1 = Charles | last1 = Bremner | first2 = David | last2 = Robertson | archive-date = 2011-09-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110923011128/http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/life_and_style/education/good_university_guide/article2166314.ece | dead-url = no }}</ref>[[伯恩茅斯藝術大學|伯恩茅斯藝術大學]]成立於2012年，提供藝術、設計和媒體相關專業。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.educationuk.org/pls/hot_bc/bc_profile.page_pls_profile_details?x=842823061811&y=0&a=0&z=6532&sec_id=26&p_lang=31 | title = Arts Institute at Bournemouth | publisher = [[British_Council|British Council]] | year = 2008 | accessdate = 29 August 2008 | archive-date = 2012-02-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120225170101/http://www.educationuk.org/pls/hot_bc/bc_profile.page_pls_profile_details?x=842823061811&y=0&a=0&z=6532&sec_id=26&p_lang=31 | dead-url = no }}</ref>

